  );
};
// bindings: 3 (items, base, PROCESSING_FEE-ref); invocations: ~7 (baseTotal, Math.ceil, itemSurchargesTotal, firstInsuranceSurcharge, +, +, +)
// Mass ≈ 3 + 14 = 17
```

