**Mass trade-off**: +3 total local mass — accepted because Rule 2 outranks APP.

**Naming**: `firstInsuranceSurcharge` mirrors the spec language ("first-insurance surcharge"). Other names re-evaluated and kept — all still describe their current behavior accurately.

